resources.string: You were an honored soldier, but no one knew about the mine under your foot.
You served with honor. The country will never forget your heroism.
This ending is not achieved yet.
You tried your best. But life did its thing.
You placed treasure over your homeland. But you lived a life of dreams.
"There are no more endings. New endings will come soon. "
Not every hero is remembered. You became proof of this.
